{"tid":1702331,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"民意大過天 唔好失民意","createTime":"2019-11-09T15:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T02:10:24.000Z","uid":13333,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c559c5f25686d334a7faef903f37a934d9fe802e","tid":1702331,"uid":13333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZZX4DZ2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZZX4DZ2.jpg&h=8656d8d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n四眼哥哥講得真係好啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望各位將呢張相 呢一句 呢個心態揚開佢<br />\n希望可以係各大平台都見到呢張相<br />\n等大家認識到四眼哥<br />\n千祈唔好起佢底 唔好誤會<br />\n文字冇表情 冇講反話 千萬不要誤會小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe285d8103908af0a10c93bcd0bad470e805411","tid":1702331,"uid":13333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:41:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"681a39667480133a149629402f9be818d534d380","tid":1702331,"uid":13333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:43:33.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"294484059ada43ff7d6685776f87a6a20178d826","tid":1702331,"uid":89514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:44:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"59abfb22c1f41d30f56de5730336eebed3b08987","tid":1702331,"uid":307389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:45:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f813eece03d9c3eaedceb789f2704f76efb34816","tid":1702331,"uid":13333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:50:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3416eca9a1bdeac89b5758bc21cb44b747b07c19","tid":1702331,"uid":13333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T15:52:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f70a81c9d4fb96a90fe6264ec72735c219df0b00","tid":1702331,"uid":13333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-1