hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpmsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=2d648b7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpmsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=63705ee9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd9b7c3865eeaaf135c8d00f66d72fcf54d5f9f0","tid":1702331,"uid":13333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T01:40:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc0227b3ec9f8dcbc42bef5f154b0fcd81a65919","tid":1702331,"uid":13333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T01:45:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b7595b1adf5604a52959c3da0208c45b8c151c6","tid":1702331,"uid":206617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T01:51:44.000Z","msg":"歡迎佢用自己既血，係第一線去頂住班發顛藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁就可以幫我地贏盡民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n